The form of the metal, stored in three barrels, has not been released.

Silver was also being carried in the truck, which was stopped near mile marker 114 on the highway. 

Locks on the back of the truck were sawed off, according to WITN.  

The Federal Bureau of Investigation has joined in the search for the robbers, thought to be male and possibly Hispanic.  

